.SH NAME
Alien::Build::Plugin::Gather::IsolateDynamic \- Plugin to gather dynamic libraries into a separate directory
.SH VERSION
.IX Header "VERSION"
version 2.80
.SH SYNOPSIS
.IX Header "SYNOPSIS"
.Vb 2
\& use alienfile;
\& plugin \*(AqGather::IsolateDynamic\*(Aq;
.Ve
.SH DESCRIPTION
.IX Header "DESCRIPTION"
This plugin moves dynamic libraries from the \f(CW\*(C`lib\*(C'\fR and \f(CW\*(C`bin\*(C'\fR directories and puts them in
their own \f(CW\*(C`dynamic\*(C'\fR directory.  This allows them to be used by FFI modules, but to be ignored
by XS modules.
.PP
This plugin provides the equivalent functionality of the \f(CW\*(C`alien_isolate_dynamic\*(C'\fR attribute
from Alien::Base::ModuleBuild.
